name: DreamerDAO
description:
This donation event is an initiative of the World Peace Artists Union and DreamerDAO.
, including more than 500 renowned artists around the world,some of their artworks were almost sold as the price of up to millions of dollars for each piece .The purpose of this funding is to build a prosperous and active NFT ecosystem which will benefit all the participants.

the contributors will get $DM governance tokens proportionally and also one NFT airdrop designed by the renowned artists if donate more than 0.1 ETH.
